<h2 class="bac"><img class="popen" src="../images/clear.gif" alt="Show information" title="Show information">Overview</h2>
<div>
<p class="bac nobr">As an intern within Global Treasury Solutions you will:</p>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>Establish excellent relationships with clients and prospective clients, often being the first point of contact for queries</li>
	<li>Take part in client / prospective client visits to grow and win new business. Prepare - and eventually deliver -proposals and presentations to clients</li>
	<li>Ensure an effective hand over process to the Bank&#39;s implementation team when new business is won, maintaining contact through the process to ensure the client&#39;s needs are met</li>
	<li>Have the drive and tenacity to follow up client queries with the necessary administration to achieve efficient client service</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

